<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 09:14:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>监管机构表示，特斯拉将为超过 120 万辆进口和中国制造的汽车修复软件</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-software-over-12-million-imported-china-made-cars-says-regulator-2025-01-24/</link><description>中国市场监管机构称，特斯拉将对部分进口Model S和X以及国产Model 3和Y汽车的安全隐患进行软件修复，总计超过120万辆。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 08:03:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-fix-software-over-12-million-imported-china-made-cars-says-regulator-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>日本外务省称，涉嫌杀害日本男学生的凶手在中国受审</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/alleged-killer-japanese-schoolboy-goes-trial-china-say-japans-foreign-ministry-2025-01-24/</link><description>日本外务省表示，对中国深圳一所日本学校就读男孩的涉嫌凶手的审判于周五在该市开始。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 08:01:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/alleged-killer-japanese-schoolboy-goes-trial-china-say-japans-foreign-ministry-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>股息激增标志着中国市场文化的转变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/dividend-surge-signals-culture-shift-chinas-markets-2025-01-24/</link><description>随着企业在北京的要求下回购股票并向等待迄今为止难以捉摸的反弹的投资者支付创纪录的股息，中国陷入困境的股市正在出现新的资本主义色彩。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 07:50:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/dividend-surge-signals-culture-shift-chinas-markets-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>在对经济的担忧中，中国准备迎接农历新年</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-readies-lunar-new-year-amid-worries-about-economy-2025-01-24/</link><description>周五，旅客们涌入火车站和机场，提着大行李箱和水果等礼物，与数百万中国人一起返回家乡，与家人一起庆祝农历新年。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 07:40:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-readies-lunar-new-year-amid-worries-about-economy-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>Burberry 受到美国消费者的节日推动</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/burberrys-quarterly-sales-drop-less-than-feared-2025-01-24/</link><description>Burberry 周五公布，受美国节日季强劲推动，季度可比商店销售额下降 4%，低于预期，这是该英国奢侈品牌扭亏为盈的举措中迈出的令人鼓舞的一步。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 07:10:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/burberrys-quarterly-sales-drop-less-than-feared-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国刺激计划将2024年消费增长提升1个百分点</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-stimulus-scheme-lifted-2024-consumption-growth-by-1-pct-point-2025-01-24/</link><description>商务部副部长盛秋平周五表示，中国的消费品以旧换新刺激计划使去年的消费增长提高了1个百分点以上，当局今年将扩大该计划。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 06:10:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-stimulus-scheme-lifted-2024-consumption-growth-by-1-pct-point-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>高级安全官员称，美国“堤丰”导弹目前将留在菲律宾</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-says-us-missile-deployment-boost-readiness-help-regional-2025-01-24/</link><description>小费迪南德·马科斯总统的国家安全顾问周五表示，美军可发射多用途导弹、射程可达数千公里的“堤丰”发射器将暂时留在菲律宾。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 05:49:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-military-says-us-missile-deployment-boost-readiness-help-regional-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国主要港口在假期前遭遇拥堵，特朗普关税威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/major-chinese-port-hit-by-congestion-ahead-holiday-trump-tariff-threat-2025-01-24/</link><description>本周，在为期八天的农历新年假期之前以及美国可能对中国商品征收一波关税之前，出口商争先恐后地从世界上最大的集装箱港口之一深圳盐田港装货和发运货物。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 05:42:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/major-chinese-port-hit-by-congestion-ahead-holiday-trump-tariff-threat-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>早间竞价：特朗普上任第一周对中国态度宽松</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-01-24/</link><description>汤姆·威斯布鲁克 (Tom Westbrook) 对欧洲和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 05:33:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/global-markets-view-europe-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国中小学加强科学教育</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-primary-secondary-schools-beef-up-science-education-2025-01-24/</link><description>中国教育部告诉中小学，他们必须加强科学教育，因为世界第二大经济体希望推动科技创新，创造新的增长点。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 03:47:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-primary-secondary-schools-beef-up-science-education-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普表示他可以与中国达成贸易协议，并称与习近平的会谈“友好”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-he-could-reach-trade-deal-with-china-calls-talk-with-xi-friendly-2025-01-24/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他上周与中国国家主席习近平的对话是友好的，他认为可以与中国达成贸易协议。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 02:48:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-he-could-reach-trade-deal-with-china-calls-talk-with-xi-friendly-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普表示他将与朝鲜金正恩接触</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-he-will-reach-out-north-koreas-kim-2025-01-24/</link><description>美国总统唐纳德·特朗普在周四播出的采访中表示，在特朗普第一任期内与朝鲜领导人金正恩建立了工作关系后，他计划寻求与朝鲜领导人金正恩重新接触。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 02:33:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-says-he-will-reach-out-north-koreas-kim-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>受特朗普能源政策影响，油价本周将下跌</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-falls-prospect-trump-pushing-up-crude-supplies-2025-01-24/</link><description>周五油价变化不大，但在美国总统唐纳德·特朗普发布全面提高美国产量的计划并要求欧佩克降低原油价格后，油价每周下跌。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 01:59:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-falls-prospect-trump-pushing-up-crude-supplies-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>日元因日本央行加息而上涨，美元因特朗普对中国的态度软化而下滑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-guard-ahead-boj-decision-dollar-set-weekly-loss-2025-01-24/</link><description>该决定发布后不久，日元在波动性的交易中波动。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 01:32:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/yen-guard-ahead-boj-decision-dollar-set-weekly-loss-2025-01-24/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉在中国推出几周后在美国、加拿大和欧洲推出新款 Model Y</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-announces-revamped-model-y-version-us-priced-59990-2025-01-24/</link><description>埃隆·马斯克 (Elon Musk) 旗下的特斯拉 (Tesla) 周四在美国、加拿大和欧洲推出了其最畅销汽车 Model Y 的新高价版本，距该车型在中国首次发布几周后。</description><pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 01:28:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/tesla-announces-revamped-model-y-version-us-priced-59990-2025-01-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>